data.description: FHA ASSUMABLE LOAN AT 3.25%! Welcome to this charming and updated home, located in desirable Buckner Terrace. Situated on a spacious lot with a large yard, this home boasts the perfect blend of modern comfort and timeless appeal. As you approach, the distinctive bay windows provide an abundance of natural light that graces the interior, creating a warm and welcoming ambiance. The updated design seamlessly marries the classic ranch-style architecture with contemporary features. The kitchen showcases modern appliances, sleek countertops, and ample cabinet space. Adjacent to the kitchen is a cozy dining area, ideal for casual or formal dining experiences. Step outside into the expansive backyard, a true oasis for outdoor enthusiasts and garden lovers.
